# Word Game

A fun and interactive word game built with Next.js and Tailwind CSS. Create words using available letters, earn points, and beat the clock!

## Features

- Create words using available letters
- Points system based on word length
- 30-second timer with time bonuses
- Level progression with new letters
- Keyboard and mouse input support
- Interactive animations and visual feedback
- Demo mode showing game mechanics

## Getting Started

1. Clone the repository
2. Install dependencies:
   ```bash
   npm install
   ```
3. Run the development server:
   ```bash
   npm run dev
   ```
4. Open [http://localhost:3000](http://localhost:3000) in your browser

## Game Rules

- Create words using the available letters
- Longer words earn more points
- Each word adds time to the clock
- Make 10 words to win
- New letters are added every 3 words
- Use keyboard or click letters to play

## Technologies Used

- Next.js
- React
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS 